<plot>On their journey from a funeral to the cemetery, which somehow takes a lifetime, a car full of Jewish relatives, talk, banter, argue and gossip revealing bittersweet, poignant family memories. Each character eventually exits the car to begin their metaphorical passage to another life, leaving the matriarch standing at the gates of Waldheim. Will she walk in?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?646498</url></doc>
